    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed at MRL 2. Validation evidence supports use of the CFD model to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The model inputs dataset reflects the Q4 2025 configuration freeze; re-validation incorporating the February 2026 model revision is planned and does not affect the current decision given the minor nature of the impeller clearance update.",
